  ('social-worker-moex-02219', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '若某方案之服務目標（objective）陳述為：「家長能夠透過機構所提供為期三個月之親職教育課程的學習， 了解自己在教養學齡期子女時所處的困境，並學會各種適當的教養方法來和子女相處」，上述陳述句未 包含下列那個概念？', '["時間架構", "改變之標的", "欲達成的結果", "測量結果之判準"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02220', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '一般而言，服務方案設計與規劃的邏輯模式中包含了：輸入、過程、輸出、成果、效應等五種構成要項。 執行方案所必須實施的各種處置方法和工作項目屬於何種要項？', '["過程", "輸出", "成果", "輸入"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02221', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '若某社會福利機構在編列與設計預算時，所採用的是將過去的預算過程及決策進行適度的延伸，則下列 何者為此一機構所使用的預算設計過程模式？', '["理性規劃模式", "漸進增值模式", "政治模式", "菁英決策模式"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02222', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '「申請者為有效完成工作需具備之知識、技術與能力」此為下列何者之定義？', '["工作規範（job specification）", "工作分析（job analysis）", "工作聲明（job announcement）", "工作條件（working conditions）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
